  "texts": [
    "The update gate indicates how much of the previous cell contents to maintain.",
    "The reset gate defines how to incorporate the new input with the previous cell contents.",
    "A GRU can model a standard RNN simply by setting the reset gate to 1 and the update gate to 0.",
    "It is simpler than the LSTM, can be trained more quickly, and can be more efficient in its execution.",
    "However, LSTM can be more expressive and with more data can lead to better results [86]."
